        <a href="/#calculator">home generator sizing calculator</a>, then review
        your results alongside our
        <a href="/generator-sizing-guide">Home Generator Sizing Guide</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Still have questions? Visit our <a href="/faqs">Generator FAQs</a>.
      </p>
